<div style='direction:ltr;border-width:100%'>

<div style='direction:ltr;margin-top:0in;margin-left:0in;width:9.0319in'>

<div style='direction:ltr;margin-top:0in;margin-left:0in;width:9.0319in'>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MySQL 8.0 </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>后支持隐藏索引（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>invisible index</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>），主要用于测试索引删除后产生的查询性能影响。索引隐藏适用于除主键索引（显示或者隐式设置）之外的索引，而主键索引不能通过任何方式隐藏。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MySQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>数据库默认创建的索引都是可见的，要显式控制一个索引的可见性，可以在
     </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;
     color:#2E75B5'>CREATE TABLE</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>，</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#2E75B5'>CREATE INDEX </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>或 </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:#2E75B5'>ALTER
     TABLE </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的索引定义命令中使用
     </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;
     color:#2E75B5'>VISIBLE </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>或 </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#2E75B5'>INVISIBLE </span><span style='font-family:
     "Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>关键字。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;
color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#BFBFBF'><span lang=zh-CN>CREATE TABLE</span><span lang=en-US>
user</span><span lang=zh-CN> (</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#BFBFBF' lang=en-US>id INT PRIMARY KEY,</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#BFBFBF' lang=en-US>name VARCHAR(25),</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#BFBFBF'>age INT,</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#BFBFBF'>weight INT,</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#2E75B5' lang=zh-CN>INDEX </span><span lang=en-US>name</span><span
lang=zh-CN>_idx (</span><span lang=en-US>name</span><span lang=zh-CN>) </span><span
style='color:#2E75B5' lang=zh-CN>INVISIBLE</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#BFBFBF'>) ENGINE = InnoDB;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#2E75B5' lang=zh-CN>ALTER TABLE </span><span
lang=en-US>user</span><span lang=zh-CN> </span><span style='color:#2E75B5'
lang=zh-CN>ADD INDEX </span><span lang=en-US>age</span><span lang=zh-CN>_idx (</span><span
lang=en-US>age</span><span lang=zh-CN>) </span><span style='color:#2E75B5'
lang=zh-CN>INVISIBLE</span><span lang=zh-CN>;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#2E75B5' lang=zh-CN>CREATE INDEX</span><span
lang=zh-CN> weight_idx </span><span style='color:#2E75B5' lang=zh-CN>ON </span><span
lang=en-US>user</span><span lang=zh-CN> (weight) </span><span style='color:
#2E75B5' lang=zh-CN>INVISIBLE</span><span lang=zh-CN>;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>系统变量</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> optimizer_switch </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>
     use_invisible_indexes </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>值控制了优化器执行计划构建时是否使用隐藏后的索引。当索引隐藏不被优化器所使用时，用于索引的软删除。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;
color:black'><span style='font-weight:bold'>语法</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#2E75B5' lang=en-US>SET</span><span lang=zh-CN>
optimizer_switch=</span><span style='color:#70AD47' lang=zh-CN>'use_invisible_indexes=on'</span><span
lang=zh-CN>;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#2E75B5' lang=en-US>SET</span><span lang=zh-CN>
optimizer_switch=</span><span style='color:#70AD47' lang=zh-CN>'use_invisible_indexes=o</span><span
style='color:#70AD47' lang=en-US>ff</span><span style='color:#70AD47'
lang=zh-CN>'</span><span lang=zh-CN>;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'><span
  style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span></span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>打开状态，隐藏索引仍然保持不可见，但优化器会把隐藏索引加入到执行计划的构建中。</span></p>
  </td>

</div>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>利用索引隐藏快速测试删除索引后对</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>查询性能的影响，而无需进行索引删除、重建操作。如果需要该索引，再设置可见就好了，这在大表测试中无疑非常有用，因为对于大表索引的删除和重新添加很耗性能，甚至影响表的正常工作。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引隐藏后，如果想要在某条单个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>查询语句上对优化器启用，可以使用</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SET_VAR </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>优化器提示来临时更新</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> optimizer_switch </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的值，如下所示：</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;
color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#2E75B5'>SELECT </p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span lang=zh-CN>SET_VAR(optimizer_switch = 'use_invisible_indexes=on')</span><span
lang=en-US> </span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>age, </p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span lang=en-US>name</span><span lang=zh-CN> </span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span lang=zh-CN>FROM </span><span lang=en-US>user</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt' lang=en-US>…</p>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>注</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>虽然索引隐藏不会被优化器使用，但仍然需要进行维护</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引的可见性不会影响索引的自身维护，例如，不管索引是可见还是不可见，每次表数据行的更改索引都会更新，并且唯一索引也可防止插入重复数据。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>没有显式主键的表如果在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> NOT NULL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>列上有任何一个唯一索引，则仍可能成为有效的隐式主键。在这种情况下，第一个这样的索引会对表数据行施加与显式主键相同的约束，并且该索引不能设置为不可见。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

 margin-bottom:0in'>
